    • Enum Constant Detail

      • administer

        public static final FileSystemEntityCapabilityOperation administer
        Administer permission. Gives the ability to modify the capabilities for a file or directory.

      • read

        public static final FileSystemEntityCapabilityOperation read
        Read permission. If set on a file, allows viewing of the information contained in the file. If set on a directory, allows access to the files and directories within. Further access is determined by the capabilities for those files and directories.

      • write

        public static final FileSystemEntityCapabilityOperation write
        Write permission. If set on a file, allows modification of the contents of the file. If set on a directory, allows adding, deleting, and renaming files.
